<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA513_05_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema513_05.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema513_05_ih_0002">
      <section class="title group">
        <h2 lang="y"><span class="pink">[1~2]</span> 그림에서 대응 관계를 찾아 식으로 나타내려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="img_box mt_20 mb_20">
        <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA513_05_IH/0001_img.png" alt="" />
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2_pink" lang="y"><img src="../../common_contents/common/img/title_heading_num_1_pink.svg" class="heading" />에서 찾은 두 양을 각각 기호로 나타내고, 두 양 사이의 대응 관계를 기호를 사용하여 식으로 나타내어 보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box">
          <div class="table_wrap">
            <table>
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col" lang="y">서로 대응하는 두 양</th>
                  <th scope="col" lang="y">기호</th>
                  <th scope="col" lang="y">대응 관계를 나타낸 식</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field></math-field>
                      <div class="example_box">
                        <p lang="y">케이크의 수</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field></math-field>
                      <div class="example_box">
                        <p>□</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td rowspan="2">
                    <div class="flex align_center justify_center gap_10">
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field></math-field>
                        <div class="example_box">
                          <p>☆</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      =
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field></math-field>
                        <div class="example_box">
                          <p>□×4</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field></math-field>
                      <div class="example_box">
                        <p lang="y">체리의 수</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field></math-field>
                      <div class="example_box">
                        <p>☆</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y" class="text_bullet">케이크의 수를 □, 체리의 수를 ☆이라고 할 때,<br />☆=□×4 또는 □=☆÷4입니다.</p>
                <p lang="y" class="text_bullet">케이크의 수를 ◇, 과자의 수를 ◎이라고 할 때,<br />◇=◎×2 또는 ◎=◇÷2입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
